{"word":"ποιητέος","slug":"ποιητέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ποιητέος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ποίησις'><el>ποίησις</el></a>\n<el>(ποιητέος, η, ον,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a>\n<p/><i>to be made</i> or <i>done</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, attic; <el>τὸ ποιητέον</el> <i>what must be done</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/>"}]}